*speech-dispatcher-0.6.2 (28 May 2007)

  28 May 2007; William Hubbs <williamh@gentoo.org>
  +files/speech-dispatcher-0.6.2-espeak.patch,
  +files/speech-dispatcher-0.6.2-python.patch,
  +speech-dispatcher-0.6.2.ebuild:
  Version bump.
  This version makes espeak the default synthesizer.

  28 Apr 2007; Sven Wegener <swegener@gentoo.org>
  speech-dispatcher-0.3.ebuild, speech-dispatcher-0.4.1.ebuild,
  speech-dispatcher-0.5.ebuild, speech-dispatcher-0.6.ebuild:
  Fix *initd and *envd calls, bug #173884.

  21 Feb 2007; <peper@gentoo.org> ChangeLog:
  Transition to Manifest2.

